Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:37.28,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯一的最愛之事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:42.09,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就是永遠在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.91,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:49.97,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}讓我心滿意足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:02.21,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯一的最愛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:07.00,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但卻難以言表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:12.43,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}偶然會感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:17.49,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仍然相信命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:22.97,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}天空的航跡雲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:29.62,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}擦過天邊的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:36.78,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只願送達昔日的淡淡思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:45.77,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:49.71,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界彷如閃耀的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:54.91,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}伴著心動的春風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:22:00.05,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}此刻  好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:04.63,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}唯一的最愛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:09.48,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但卻難以言表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:19.27,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只願守望你
